  "texts": [
    "The newest technology obtained at the end of these searches is blockchain technology.",
    "In this sense, a blockchain ledger is a decentralized and immutable digital ledger that records transactions in a chronological chain of blocks.",
    "It ensures transparency, security, and integrity by distributing the ledger across multiple participants, making it resistant to tampering and providing a trusted source of truth [3].",
    "One of a blockchain's primary goals is to past transactions.",
    "The idea of keeping track of transactions on a ledger is fundamental to the blockchain."
  ]
}